id: pm-jt3b
title: "Split search.ts (3119 LOC, 92% of 3400 cap) into rendering / query-parsing / inline-field modules"
description: "2026-07-04 code-quality sweep: src/cli/commands/search.ts is 3119 LOC vs the 3400 static-gate cap — one feature-add from failing the gate — and contains 4 sub-threshold jscpd clones internally (plus a cross-file clone with list.ts:489). Split along rendering vs query-parsing vs inline field:value syntax boundaries (the two parse layers from PR#290) to pay down both LOC and duplication."
